column1:
I slept so much that even sleep's boring now!
What doooo...?

Well, is anyone feeling peckish yet? Although
I suppose we've nearly reached Kyoto...

Don't tell me to perform for you! I ain't some
comedian.
I'll take the wheel for you.
Should I send it to voicemail?

Uhh, well... I guess there's no reason not to.
Go ahead.
Don't be stupid! Just answer for me, will you?

Wait, no! Can you just, uh, answer for me?
Sorry...

Make it quick though. Just say I'm driving, and
that I'll call back later.

The caller ID says that it's
someone named "Akane"...
It's way past noon. Where are you?

Don't tell me you forgot what day it is. We were
supposed to visit Mom's grave together.

Huh? Who is this? Please give him his phone
back.
Driving? Oh, I guess that makes sense...
Is it some kind of emergency?
Why don'tcha just pull over, Gramps?
Do I hear a bunch of girls with you?

What an asshole! You're just out partying
right now, aren't you!?

You really are the worst! Don't bother coming
home again!
You don't even deserve to visit Mom's grave!

Um, I don't know the details, but... is everything
all right?
Yeah, sorry about that... Just forget it.

Gah, dammit! Sorry, time to floor it—hang onto
your seats, kids!
